    "S5 showcases the performance comparison of DenseGNN-Lite against reference models on experimental small datasets.",
    "These datasets, sourced from matminer (https://github.com/ dhw059/DenseGNN/datasets/dataset_metadata.json), have sample sizes ranging from 100 to 3000, covering various scales of experimental data.",
